name: Dead Again
overview: The hour-long series follows a top team of detectives who will re-examine controversial murder cases in which unresolved questions still linger long after the verdict was determined.

episodes.name: Behind Closed Doors
episodes.overview: In Alliance, OH, detectives Michele Wood (Homicide Detective, Chicago), Joe Schillaci (Retired Deputy Commander, Miami), and Kevin Gannon (Retired Detective Sergeant, NYC) re-investigate the controversial murder of a young mother whose throat was slashed while her children were sleeping. They soon discover that the victim was leading a secret life. In an effort to find the truth, the detectives explore claims of a police cover up and must confront a convicted killer in prison

episodes.name: Key Witness
episodes.overview: An elite homicide team re-investigates a controversial 2008 double-murder case, starting on a meticulously reconstructred crime scene, to see if they come to the original same conclusion as the original investigators.

episodes.name: Thou Shalt Not Kill
episodes.overview: The brutal murder of a nun at a chapel in Toledo sent shock waves through the local community and an entire nation. The person convicted was as unlikely as the victim herself, and some believe that person was not the killer. Now, a team of elite investigators will re-examine this horrific crime in an attempt to shed light on what actually happened.

episodes.name: Stabbed in the Back
episodes.overview: The investigators probe the case of a Dallas art student who was stabbed to death in her sleep, and uncover a possible revenge plot when the victim's friends are interviewed.

episodes.name: Death to the Doctor
episodes.overview: The case of a doctor who was gunned down in a suspected carjacking takes a turn when the detectives take a deeper look into the victim's personal life.

episodes.name: Millionaire Murder
episodes.overview: Claims of seduction, jealousy and greed re-emerge when the detectives take a closer look at the unsolved killing of a wealthy entrepreneur.
